WITH CRT1 AS
(

select * 
from(
SELECT DISTINCT A.KEY1,A.SSEGURO,A.FIN_VIG_ACT,A.INI_VIG,CASE WHEN RN=1 THEN 0 
        WHEN RN>1 AND RENEWAL_CRITERIA=1 THEN 1
        --WHEN RN1=1 THEN 1
        ELSE 0 END AS RENEWAL_CRITERION_1,
        CASE WHEN RN1=1 THEN 'NB'
        when ini_vig=fin_vig_act  then 'NB' 
        WHEN RN1>1 AND RENEWAL_CRITERIA=1 THEN 'RB'
        WHEN RN=1 THEN 'RB'
        ELSE 'NB' END AS BUSINESS_TYPE_INDICATOR_1,
        ROW_NUMBER()OVER(PARTITION BY KEY1,SSEGURO ORDER BY FIN_VIG_ACT DESC,INI_VIG DESC,BUSINESS_TYPE_INDICATOR_1)ROWNUM
FROM(
SELECT a.key1,a.FIN_VIG_ACT,a.ini_vig,a.sseguro,ROW_NUMBER()OVER(PARTITION BY A.key1 ORDER BY A.FIN_VIG_ACT DESC,a.ini_vig desc)AS RN,
CASE WHEN B.key1 IS NOT NULL and a.sseguro<>b.sseguro THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS RENEWAL_CRITERIA,
        ROW_NUMBER()OVER(PARTITION BY A.key1 ORDER BY A.FIN_VIG_ACT asc,a.ini_vig asc)AS RN1
FROM (select ASEGURADO_RUT||CORREDOR_RUT||COB_PLAN||PATENTE as key1,
        cast(sseguro as varchar(80))as sseguro,fin_vig_act,ini_vig,endoso_agrup from cdp_dwh.base_final_liberty 
        union all 
        select ASEGURADO_RUT||CORREDOR_RUT||COB_PLAN||PATENTE as key1,
        sseguro,fin_vig_act,ini_vig,endoso_agrup from cdp_dwh.base_final_penta ) A
LEFT JOIN (select ASEGURADO_RUT||CORREDOR_RUT||COB_PLAN||PATENTE as key1,
        cast(sseguro as varchar(80))as sseguro ,fin_vig_act,ini_vig,endoso_agrup from cdp_dwh.base_final_liberty
        union all 
        select ASEGURADO_RUT||CORREDOR_RUT||COB_PLAN||PATENTE as key1,
        sseguro,fin_vig_act,ini_vig,endoso_agrup from cdp_dwh.base_final_penta) B
ON A.FIN_VIG_ACT=B.INI_VIG AND A.key1=B.key1
WHERE A.key1 IS NOT NULL 
--and A.KEY1='04095670788853001020CDGK47' --AND A.ENDOSO_AGRUP NOT IN('CANCELACION','ANULACION')  --AND B.ENDOSO_AGRUP NOT IN('CANCELACION','ANULACION')
ORDER BY A.FIN_VIG_ACT DESC,A.INI_VIG DESC)A
ORDER BY FIN_VIG_ACT DESC
)
WHERE ROWNUM=1
),

CRT2 AS
(

select * 
from(
SELECT DISTINCT A.key2,A.SSEGURO,A.FIN_VIG_ACT,A.INI_VIG,CASE WHEN RN=1 THEN 0 
        WHEN RN>1 AND RENEWAL_CRITERIA=1 THEN 1
        --WHEN RN1=1 THEN 1
        ELSE 0 END AS RENEWAL_CRITERION_2,
        CASE WHEN RN1=1 THEN 'NB' 
        when ini_vig=fin_vig_act  then 'NB'
        WHEN RN1>1 AND RENEWAL_CRITERIA=1 THEN 'RB'
        WHEN RN=1 THEN 'RB'
        ELSE 'NB' END AS BUSINESS_TYPE_INDICATOR_2,
        ROW_NUMBER()OVER(PARTITION BY key2,SSEGURO ORDER BY FIN_VIG_ACT DESC,INI_VIG DESC,BUSINESS_TYPE_INDICATOR_2)ROWNUM
FROM(
SELECT a.key2,a.FIN_VIG_ACT,a.ini_vig,a.sseguro,ROW_NUMBER()OVER(PARTITION BY A.key2 ORDER BY A.FIN_VIG_ACT DESC,a.ini_vig desc)AS RN,
CASE WHEN B.key2 IS NOT NULL and a.sseguro<>b.sseguro THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS RENEWAL_CRITERIA,
        ROW_NUMBER()OVER(PARTITION BY A.key2 ORDER BY A.FIN_VIG_ACT asc,a.ini_vig asc)AS RN1
FROM (select ASEGURADO_RUT||CORREDOR_RUT||COB_PLAN||NUM_MOTOR as key2,
        cast(sseguro as varchar(80))as sseguro,fin_vig_act,ini_vig,endoso_agrup from cdp_dwh.base_final_liberty 
        union all 
        select ASEGURADO_RUT||CORREDOR_RUT||COB_PLAN||NUM_MOTOR as key2,
        sseguro,fin_vig_act,ini_vig,endoso_agrup from cdp_dwh.base_final_penta ) A
LEFT JOIN (select ASEGURADO_RUT||CORREDOR_RUT||COB_PLAN||NUM_MOTOR as key2,
        cast(sseguro as varchar(80))as sseguro,fin_vig_act,ini_vig,endoso_agrup from cdp_dwh.base_final_liberty 
        union all 
        select ASEGURADO_RUT||CORREDOR_RUT||COB_PLAN||NUM_MOTOR as key2,
        sseguro,fin_vig_act,ini_vig,endoso_agrup from cdp_dwh.base_final_penta ) B
ON A.FIN_VIG_ACT=B.INI_VIG AND A.key2=B.key2
WHERE A.key2 IS NOT NULL 
--and A.KEY1='04095670788853001020CDGK47' --AND A.ENDOSO_AGRUP NOT IN('CANCELACION','ANULACION')  --AND B.ENDOSO_AGRUP NOT IN('CANCELACION','ANULACION')
ORDER BY A.FIN_VIG_ACT DESC,A.INI_VIG DESC)A
ORDER BY FIN_VIG_ACT DESC
)
WHERE ROWNUM=1
),
CRT3 AS
(

select * 
from(
SELECT DISTINCT A.key3,A.SSEGURO,A.FIN_VIG_ACT,A.INI_VIG,CASE WHEN RN=1 THEN 0 
        WHEN RN>1 AND RENEWAL_CRITERIA=1 THEN 1
        --WHEN RN1=1 THEN 1
        ELSE 0 END AS RENEWAL_CRITERION_3,
        CASE WHEN RN1=1 THEN 'NB' 
        when ini_vig=fin_vig_act  then 'NB'
        WHEN RN1>1 AND RENEWAL_CRITERIA=1 THEN 'RB'
        WHEN RN=1 THEN 'RB'
        ELSE 'NB' END AS BUSINESS_TYPE_INDICATOR_3,
        ROW_NUMBER()OVER(PARTITION BY key3,SSEGURO ORDER BY FIN_VIG_ACT DESC,INI_VIG DESC,BUSINESS_TYPE_INDICATOR_3)ROWNUM
FROM(
SELECT a.key3,a.FIN_VIG_ACT,a.ini_vig,a.sseguro,ROW_NUMBER()OVER(PARTITION BY A.key3 ORDER BY A.FIN_VIG_ACT DESC,a.ini_vig desc)AS RN,
CASE WHEN B.key3 IS NOT NULL and a.sseguro<>b.sseguro THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS RENEWAL_CRITERIA,
        ROW_NUMBER()OVER(PARTITION BY A.key3 ORDER BY A.FIN_VIG_ACT asc,a.ini_vig asc)AS RN1
FROM (select ASEGURADO_RUT||CORREDOR_RUT||COB_PLAN||NRO_MASIVO as key3,
        cast(sseguro as varchar(80))as sseguro ,fin_vig_act,ini_vig,endoso_agrup from cdp_dwh.base_final_liberty 
        union all
        select ASEGURADO_RUT||CORREDOR_RUT||COB_PLAN||NRO_MASIVO as key3,
        sseguro,fin_vig_act,ini_vig,endoso_agrup from cdp_dwh.base_final_penta ) A
LEFT JOIN (select ASEGURADO_RUT||CORREDOR_RUT||COB_PLAN||NRO_MASIVO as key3,
        cast(sseguro as varchar(80))as sseguro,fin_vig_act,ini_vig,endoso_agrup from cdp_dwh.base_final_liberty 
        union all
        select ASEGURADO_RUT||CORREDOR_RUT||COB_PLAN||NRO_MASIVO as key3,
        sseguro,fin_vig_act,ini_vig,endoso_agrup from cdp_dwh.base_final_penta ) B
ON A.FIN_VIG_ACT=B.INI_VIG AND A.key3=B.key3
WHERE A.key3 IS NOT NULL 
--and A.KEY1='04095670788853001020CDGK47' --AND A.ENDOSO_AGRUP NOT IN('CANCELACION','ANULACION')  --AND B.ENDOSO_AGRUP NOT IN('CANCELACION','ANULACION')
ORDER BY A.FIN_VIG_ACT DESC,A.INI_VIG DESC)A
ORDER BY FIN_VIG_ACT DESC
)
WHERE ROWNUM=1
)

select src_sys_cd,
       policy_item_id,
       policy_num,
       policy_item_num,
       lob_cd,
       branch_office_cd,
       insured_rut_num,
       policy_issue_dt,
       policy_ori_exp_dt,
       policy_act_exp_dt,
       effective_days,
       SUBSCRIBED_DAYS,
       veh_make,
       veh_model,
       veh_class_cd,
	   Use,
	   veh_year,
	   lic_plate_num,
	   veh_type_cd,
	   veh_type_desc,
	   veh_motor_num,
	   broker_rut_num,
	   Massive_Number,
	   prd_cd,
	   pln_cd,
	   policyholder_rut_num,
	   mv_id,
	   deductible,
	   Fleet_Indicator,
	   policy_premium_amt,
	   Commission_amt,
	   mv_reason_cd,
	   group_endorsements,
	   coverage_plan,
	   business_number,
	   premium_rate_amt,
	   discount_amt,
	   mv_reason_desc,
	   anulac_dt,
	   carpro_dt,
	   policy_exp_dt,
	   Dim_broker_key,
	   Dim_LOB_key,
	   Dim_Insured_key,
	   dim_policyholder_key,
	   src.Key1,
	   src.Key2,
	   src.Key3,
	   Validity_Indicator,
	   Renewable_Product_Indicator,
	   crt1.BUSINESS_TYPE_INDICATOR_1,
	   crt2.BUSINESS_TYPE_INDICATOR_2,
	   crt3.BUSINESS_TYPE_INDICATOR_3,
	   crt1.RENEWAL_CRITERION_1 as Indicator_Renewal_Criterion_1,
	   crt2.RENEWAL_CRITERION_2 as Indicator_Renewal_Criterion_2,
	   crt3.RENEWAL_CRITERION_3 as Indicator_Renewal_Criterion_3,
	   CASE WHEN (crt1.RENEWAL_CRITERION_1=1) OR (crt2.RENEWAL_CRITERION_2=1) OR (crt3.RENEWAL_CRITERION_3=1)
	   THEN 1
	   ELSE 0
	   END AS final_Renewal_Indicator,
           tmake ,
           tmodel ,
	   LKP_MAX_KEY.max_sid
	   
From
       
(
select  
ORIGEN as src_sys_cd,
cast(final_liberty.SSEGURO as varchar(80)) as	policy_item_id,
POLIZA as	policy_num,
ITEM as	policy_item_num,
CRAMO as	lob_cd,
ID_SUCURSAL as	branch_office_cd,
ASEGURADO_RUT AS insured_rut_num,
cast(final_liberty.INI_VIG as date)as	policy_issue_dt,
cast(FIN_VIG_ORIG as date)as	policy_ori_exp_dt,
cast(final_liberty.FIN_VIG_ACT as date)  as	policy_act_exp_dt,
DIAS_VIGENTE as	effective_days,
DIAS_SUSCRITOS as SUBSCRIBED_DAYS,
VEH_CMARCA as veh_make,
VEH_CMODELO as	veh_model,
VEH_CLASE as veh_class_cd,
USO as	Use,
VEH_ANO as	veh_year,
PATENTE as	lic_plate_num,
VEH_CTIPO as	veh_type_cd,
VEH_TIPO as	veh_type_desc,
NUM_MOTOR as	veh_motor_num,
CORREDOR_RUT as broker_rut_num,
NRO_MASIVO  as	Massive_Number,
COD_PRODUCTO as	prd_cd,
COD_PLAN as	pln_cd,
CONTRATANTE_RUT as policyholder_rut_num,
cast(num_endoso as varchar(60)) as mv_id,
DEDUCIBLE as deductible,
FLOTA as Fleet_Indicator,
PRIMA as policy_premium_amt,
COMISION as	Commission_amt,
COD_ENDOSO as mv_reason_cd,
ENDOSO_AGRUP as	group_endorsements,
COB_PLAN as	coverage_plan,
0 as	business_number,
prima_tarifa as	premium_rate_amt,
descuento as discount_amt,
tdescrip as	mv_reason_desc,
cast(fanulac as date) as	anulac_dt,
cast(fcarpro as date) as	carpro_dt,
cast(fvencim as date)as	policy_exp_dt,
isnull(broker1.dim_broker_key,0) as Dim_broker_key,
lob.dim_lob_key as Dim_LOB_key,
isnull(insured.dim_insured_key,0) as Dim_Insured_key,
isnull(PH1.dim_policyholder_key,0) as dim_policyholder_key,
isnull(ASEGURADO_RUT,'') || isnull(CORREDOR_RUT,'') || isnull(cast(COB_PLAN as varchar(50)),'') || isnull(PATENTE,'') as Key1,
isnull(ASEGURADO_RUT,'') || isnull(CORREDOR_RUT,'') || isnull(cast(COB_PLAN as varchar(50)),'') || isnull(NUM_MOTOR,'') as Key2,
isnull(ASEGURADO_RUT,'') || isnull(CORREDOR_RUT,'') || isnull(cast(COB_PLAN as varchar(50)),'') || isnull(NRO_MASIVO,'') as Key3,
--ASEGURADO_RUT || CORREDOR_RUT || COB_PLAN || PATENTE as Key1,
--ASEGURADO_RUT || CORREDOR_RUT || COB_PLAN || NUM_MOTOR as Key2,
--ASEGURADO_RUT || CORREDOR_RUT || COB_PLAN || NRO_MASIVO as Key3,
case when ( DIAS_VIGENTE >=  DIAS_SUSCRITOS)AND
        final_liberty.FIN_VIG_ACT >=   FIN_VIG_ORIG AND
        ENDOSO_AGRUP NOT IN ('CANCELACION', 'ANULACION') then 1
else 0
end as Validity_Indicator,
case
when cod_producto in 
		(Select distinct renewable_product_indicator from cdp_stg_dwh.renewals_param_axis where renewable_product_indicator IS NOT NULL )
then 1 else 0
end as 
Renewable_Product_Indicator,
final_liberty.tmarca as tmake ,
final_liberty.tmodelo as tmodel 
from cdp_dwh.base_final_liberty as final_liberty

left join cdp_dwh.dim_lob_t as lob
on final_liberty.cramo=lob.lob_cd 
and lob.src_sys_cd='axis'

left join (select broker.dim_broker_key,src_sys_cd,substring(broker.broker_rut_num,1,length(broker.broker_rut_num)-1) as broker_rut_num from cdp_dwh.dim_broker_t broker
            inner join (select substring(broker_rut_num,1,length(broker_rut_num)-1) as broker_rut_num, max(dim_broker_key)as dim_broker_key from cdp_dwh.dim_broker_t
                        group by substring(broker_rut_num,1,length(broker_rut_num)-1))dim
            on broker.dim_broker_key=dim.dim_broker_key)Broker1
on final_liberty.corredor_rut = Broker1.broker_rut_num and Broker1.src_sys_cd='axis'
left join (SELECT DISTINCT dins.dim_insured_key,base.sseguro  from 
(select 
    sseguro, 
    sperson,
    coalesce(cast(cdomici as integer),0) as cdomici,
    row_number() over( partition by sseguro order by nmovima,nriesgo desc,norden desc ) rowindex
  from 
    cdp_ods.sisaxis_asegurados tase 
  where 
    ffecfin is null 
)AA
inner join cdp_stg_dwh.base_lib base
      on base.sseguro = AA.sseguro
      and AA.rowindex = 1
left outer join cdp_dwh.dim_insured_t dins
      on AA.sperson = dins.insured_id
      and AA.cdomici = dins.address_id
      and dins.src_sys_cd = 'axis'
)insured
ON final_liberty.SSEGURO=insured.sseguro
left join 
(SELECT DISTINCT 
POL_HOLD.dim_policyholder_key,sseguro  from 
(SELECT AA.policyholder_id, sseguro,POL_HOLD.dim_policyholder_key FROM
(select 
    base.sseguro,
    ttom.sperson, 
    ttom.cdomici, 
    cast(cast(ttom.sperson as decimal(11,0)) as varchar) || '-' || cast(cast(ttom.cdomici as decimal(7,0)) as varchar) as policyholder_id 
  from 
    cdp_stg_dwh.base_lib base
    left outer join cdp_ods.sisaxis_seguros tse1
      on base.poliza = tse1.npoliza
      and tse1.ncertif = 0
    left outer join cdp_ods.sisaxis_tomadores ttom 
      on tse1.sseguro = ttom.sseguro 
)AA
INNER JOIN cdp_dwh.dim_policyholder_t POL_HOLD
ON AA.policyholder_id=POL_HOLD.policyholder_id
AND POL_HOLD.src_sys_cd='axis'
)POL_HOLD )PH1
ON final_liberty.SSEGURO=PH1.sseguro


union all

select 
ORIGEN as src_sys_cd,
final_penta.SSEGURO as policy_item_id,
POLIZA as policy_num,
ITEM as	policy_item_num,
CRAMO as lob_cd,
ID_SUCURSAL as	branch_office_cd,
cast(ASEGURADO_RUT as varchar(42)) as insured_rut_num,
cast(final_penta. INI_VIG as date) as policy_issue_dt,
cast(FIN_VIG_ORIG as date) as	policy_ori_exp_dt,
cast(final_penta.FIN_VIG_ACT as date) as	policy_act_exp_dt,
DIAS_VIGENTE as	effective_days,
DIAS_SUSCRITOS as SUBSCRIBED_DAYS,
cast(VEH_CMARCA as varchar(15)) as veh_make,
VEH_CMODELO as	veh_model,
cast(VEH_CLASE as varchar(9)) as veh_class_cd,
USO as	Use,
VEH_ANO as veh_year,
PATENTE as lic_plate_num,
cast(VEH_CTIPO as varchar(15))as veh_type_cd,
VEH_TIPO as veh_type_desc,
NUM_MOTOR as veh_motor_num,
cast(CORREDOR_RUT as varchar(42)) as broker_rut_num,
NRO_MASIVO as Massive_Number,
COD_PRODUCTO as	prd_cd,
COD_PLAN as pln_cd,
cast(CONTRATANTE_RUT as varchar(42)) as policyholder_rut_num,
null as mv_id,
cast(DEDUCIBLE as numeric(25,10)) as deductible,
FLOTA as Fleet_Indicator,
PRIMA as	policy_premium_amt,
COMISION as	Commission_amt,
COD_ENDOSO as	mv_reason_cd,
ENDOSO_AGRUP as	group_endorsements,
COB_PLAN as	coverage_plan,
NUM_NEG  as	business_number,
0  as premium_rate_amt,
0  as discount_amt,
null  as	mv_reason_desc,
null  as	anulac_dt,
null as	carpro_dt,
null  as	policy_exp_dt,
isnull(broker1.dim_broker_key,0) as Dim_broker_key,
lob.dim_lob_key as Dim_LOB_key,
isnull(ins.dim_insured_key,0) as Dim_Insured_key,
isnull(PH1.dim_policyholder_key,0) as dim_policyholder_key,
isnull(cast(ASEGURADO_RUT as varchar(60)),'') || isnull(cast(CORREDOR_RUT as varchar(60)),'') || isnull(cast(COB_PLAN as varchar(30)),'') || isnull(PATENTE,'') as Key1,
isnull(cast(ASEGURADO_RUT as varchar(60)),'') || isnull(cast(CORREDOR_RUT as varchar(60)),'') || isnull(cast(COB_PLAN as varchar(30)),'') || isnull(NUM_MOTOR,'') as Key2,
isnull(cast(ASEGURADO_RUT as varchar(60)),'') || isnull(cast(CORREDOR_RUT as varchar(60)),'') || isnull(cast(COB_PLAN as varchar(30)),'') || isnull(NRO_MASIVO,'') as Key3,
--ASEGURADO_RUT || CORREDOR_RUT || COB_PLAN || PATENTE as Key1,
--ASEGURADO_RUT || CORREDOR_RUT || COB_PLAN || NUM_MOTOR as Key2,
--ASEGURADO_RUT || CORREDOR_RUT || COB_PLAN || NRO_MASIVO as Key3,
case when ( DIAS_VIGENTE >=  DIAS_SUSCRITOS)AND
        final_penta.FIN_VIG_ACT >=   FIN_VIG_ORIG AND
        ENDOSO_AGRUP NOT IN ('CANCELACION', 'ANULACION') then 1
else 0
end as Validity_Indicator,
case
when cod_producto in (1,3,8,10,11,13,14,16,22,26,28,31,33,36,38,70,20020,20022,20024,20026,20034,20280,20285,20290,20300)
then 0 else 1
end as 
Renewable_Product_Indicator,
final_penta.tmarca as tmake ,
final_penta.tmodelo as tmodel 
from cdp_dwh.base_final_penta as final_penta
left join cdp_dwh.dim_lob_t as lob
on final_penta.cramo=lob.lob_cd 
and lob.src_sys_cd='penta'
left join cdp_dwh.dim_broker_t Broker1
on final_penta.corredor_rut = substring(broker_rut_num,1,length(broker_rut_num)-1) 
and Broker1.src_sys_cd='axis'
left join (select insured.dim_insured_key,src_sys_cd, insured.insured_rut_num from cdp_dwh.dim_insured_t insured
            inner join (select insured_rut_num, max(dim_insured_key)as dim_insured_key from cdp_dwh.dim_insured_t
                        group by insured_rut_num)dim
            on insured.dim_insured_key=dim.dim_insured_key)ins
on final_penta.asegurado_rut = ins.insured_rut_num  and ins.src_sys_cd='penta' 

left join (select PH.dim_policyholder_key,src_sys_cd, PH.policyholder_rut_num from cdp_dwh.dim_policyholder_t PH
             inner join (select policyholder_rut_num, max(dim_policyholder_key)as dim_policyholder_key from cdp_dwh.dim_policyholder_t
                        group by policyholder_rut_num)dim
             on PH.dim_policyholder_key=dim.dim_policyholder_key)PH1
on final_penta.contratante_rut = PH1.policyholder_rut_num and PH1.src_sys_cd='penta'
)src
left join crt1
on src.policy_item_id=crt1.sseguro
left join crt2
on src.policy_item_id=crt2.sseguro
left join crt3
on src.policy_item_id=crt3.sseguro
left outer join 
(select 1 dummy,max(fact_renewals_key) max_sid  from  cdp_dwh.fact_renewals_t ) LKP_MAX_KEY
on LKP_MAX_KEY.dummy=1

SELECT fact_renewals_key,cast(policy_item_id as varchar(80))as policy_item_id,src_sys_cd,rec_crt_dtm
from cdp_dwh.fact_renewals_t
